    "method": [
        {
            "text": "Add the rice and water to a pan and cook until no liquid is left",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Start boiling the milk, cinnamon, vanilla and zest in another pan",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Add the boiled milk and stuff to the rice and place on a medium heat",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Stir with a wooden spoon regularly until it boils. From here on it must be stirred continuously",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "When the mixture becomes thick (leaves a trail on the spoon), gradually add the butter",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Once the butter is well incorporated, remove the rice from the heat and let the temperature drop slightly",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Sprinkle in the salt and <span class=\"quantity\">300</span>g of sugar while stirring(whisking is probably too rough)",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Taste and see if it needs more sugar. While hot, it should taste a little too sweet",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "If using alcohol, stir it in now",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        },
        {
            "text": "Leave to cool",
            "post_notes": [],
            "pre_notes": [],
            "type": "METHOD_STEP"
        }
    ],
    "notes": [
        {
            "text": "Next time, weigh the milk rice before and after cooking to see how much milk needs to evaporate to give good texture",
